tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE Assignments (
    assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    teacher_id INT,
    feedback TEXT,
    grade FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE Assignments (
    assignment_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    student_id INT,
    teacher_id INT,
    assignment_name VARCHAR(255),
    feedback TEXT,
    grade INT
);

CREATE TABLE Assignments (
  assignment_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  student_id UUID,
  teacher_id UUID,
  feedback TEXT,
  grade FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE Students (
  student_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name TEXT,
  last_name TEXT,
  email TEXT,
  class_id UUID
)

CREATE TABLE Teachers (
  teacher_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  first_name TEXT,
  last_name TEXT,
  email TEXT,
  department TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE Classes (
  class_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  class_name TEXT,
  class_code TEXT,
  teacher_id UUID
)

CREATE TABLE Feedback (
  feedback_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  assignment_id UUID,
  student_id UUID,
  teacher_id UUID,
  feedback_text TEXT
)
